e\">Scott Benner.<\/span><\/a><\/p>","font_size":4,"text_columns":1,"align_text":"text-left","button_text":"","button_url":"","button_color":"btn--neutral","button_style":"btn-text-thick-line","text_color":"text--neutral","bg_color":""}}},"block_order":["text_WaVeKB","text_8XnPic"],"name":"Custom content","settings":{"height":"use_screen_one_fifth","brick_gutter":20,"borders":false,"vertalign":"valign--top","bg_color":"","preload_image":false,"width":"wrapper","padding_top":36,"padding_bottom":0}},"section_custom_content_mHhkdw":{"type":"section-custom-content","blocks":{"text_WBbNYj":{"type":"text","settings":{"kicker":"key takeaways","enable_line":true,"kicker_text_size":5,"title":"","text":"<ul><li>Bain Capital extended its commitment to inclusive art across locations by acquiring original works for its NYC office, enhancing both its workplace environment and social impact strategy.<\/li><li>The investment provided ArtLifting artists with financial support and professional visibility. <\/li><\/ul>","font_size":4,"text_columns":1,"align_text":"text-left","button_text":"","button_url":"","button_color":"btn--neutral","button_style":"btn-text-thick-line","text_color":"text--neutral","bg_color":""}}},"block_order":["text_WBbNYj"],"name":"Custom content","settings":{"height":"use_screen_one_fifth","brick_gutter":20,"borders":false,"vertalign":"valign--top","bg_color":"","preload_image":false,"width":"wrapper","padding_top":36,"padding_bottom":0}},"section_richtext_CBpRyR":{"type":"section-richtext","blocks":{"heading_ziYQec":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Art brings visual and social impact to the workplace","text_size":8}},"text_VWWYX7":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Headquartered in Boston, Bain Capital is a leading private, multi-asset investment firm. Since 2016, Bain Capital has acquired a diverse selection of artwork for multiple offices.<\/p><p>To infuse social impact throughout their NYC offices — including their 15,000-square-foot space on Madison Avenue — Bain Capital  acquired artwork by <a href=\"\/collections\/marc\" title=\"Marc (he\/him\/his)\">Marc<\/a>, <a href=\"\/collections\/christina-constantine\" title=\"Christina Constantine (she\/her\/hers)\">Christina Constantine<\/a>, and <a href=\"\/collections\/scott-benner\" title=\"Scott Benner (he\/him\/his)\">Scott Benner<\/a>. The significant investment in original artwork by emerging contemporary artists created lasting impacts for the artists and Bain Capital’s art collection.<\/p><p>Upon learning about the sizable acquisition, ArtLifting artist Marc, shared, “Bain Capital has given me freedom to explore and capitalize on my next chapter. Hard to put into words what Bain has afforded me. Sincere thanks and gratitude come to mind quickly but doesn’t seem to say enough. You have given me a new life, one beyond approach. I am forever indebted to you. Thank you!”<\/p><p>Bain Capital's decision to feature artwork by ArtLifting artists isn't just about aesthetics—it's a statement of values, reflecting their commitment to social impact while fostering an inclusive workplace culture that sees the potential in everyone.<\/p><p>Bain Capital's comprehensive art strategy supports inclusive environments at multiple office locations, including their Boston headquarters. <a href=\"\/blogs\/portfolio\/bain-capital-hq\" title=\"Bain Capital HQ\">Read about our Boston HQ project here<\/a>. <\/p>","text_size":4,"text_columns":1}},"text_i4Enrp":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<h5>\"Sometimes the story behind the art is as compelling as the art itself.\"<\/h5><p><br\/>-Deval Patrick, former governor of Massachusetts and advisor at Bain Capital Double<\/p>","text_size":4,"text_columns":1}},"text_jjhxmP":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p><strong>Images<\/strong><\/p><ol><li>Three paintings by <a href=\"\/collections\/marc\" title=\"Marc (he\/him\/his)\">Marc<\/a> hang above a seating area.<\/li><li>Three paintings by <a href=\"\/collections\/marc\" title=\"Marc (he\/him\/his)\">Marc<\/a> hang in a hallway.<\/li><li>Four canvas prints by <a href=\"\/collections\/scott-benner\" title=\"Scott Benner (he\/him\/his)\">Scott Benner<\/a> hang on a white wall.<\/li><li>Three canvas prints by <a href=\"\/collections\/christina-constantine\" title=\"Christina Constantine (she\/her\/hers)\">Christina Constantine<\/a> hang in a conference room avove a console.<\/li><li>A painting by <a href=\"\/collections\/marc\" title=\"Marc (he\/him\/his)\">Marc<\/a> hangs in a conference room.<\/li><li>A painting by <a href=\"\/collections\/marc\" title=\"Marc (he\/him\/his)\">Marc<\/a> hangs above a desk.<\/li><li>Two paintings by <a href=\"\/collections\/marc\" title=\"Marc (he\/him\/his)\">Marc<\/a> hang on a white wall.<\/li><li>Two paintings by <a href=\"\/collections\/marc\" title=\"Marc (he\/him\/his)\">Marc<\/a> hang on a white wall.<\/li><li>A painting by <a href=\"\/collections\/marc\" title=\"Marc (he\/him\/his)\">Marc<\/a> hangs on a white wall.<\/li><li>An artwork by <a href=\"\/collections\/christina-constantine\" title=\"Christina Constantine (she\/her\/hers)\">Christina Constantine<\/a> hangs on a white wall.<\/li><li>Two paintings by <a href=\"\/collections\/marc\" title=\"Marc (he\/him\/his)\">Marc<\/a> hang in above a seating area.<\/li><\/ol>","text_size":4,"text_columns":1}}},"block_order":["heading_ziYQec","text_VWWYX7","text_i4Enrp","text_jjhxmP"],"settings":{"align_text":"text-left","text_color":"text--neutral","bg":"palette--light bg--neutral","content_width":850,"width":"wrapper","padding_top":36,"padding_bottom":36}},"section_contact_nRHrHF":{"type":"section-contact","blocks":{"select_QzKLrA":{"type":"select","settings":{"title":"Topic","required":true,"label_one":"General Inquiries","label_two":"Consumer Sales","label_three":"Corporate Sales","label_four":"Artists","label_five":"Partnerships","label_six":""}},"email_KepGKR":{"type":"email","settings":{"title":"Name","required":true}},"text_QzTHDz":{"type":"text","sett